## ğŸ“Š API Endpoints Reference

### Core Endpoints
- `GET /` - Original UI
- `GET /dashboard` - World-class dashboard
- `GET /api/health` - Health check

### TwelveData Monitoring (3 endpoints)
- `GET /api/twelvedata/status` - API health & metrics
- `GET /api/twelvedata/symbols` - Per-symbol status
- `POST /api/twelvedata/refresh` - Force refresh data

### Data Quality (3 endpoints)
- `POST /api/quality/assess` - Assess single symbol (0-100)
- `GET /api/quality/system` - System-wide quality report
- `GET /api/quality/startup` - Quick startup validation

### Timeframe Engine (4 endpoints)
- `GET /api/timeframes/available` - Valid timeframes from 5m base
- `POST /api/timeframes/calculate` - Calculate custom timeframe
- `POST /api/timeframes/resample` - Resample to target timeframe
- `GET /api/timeframes/recommend` - Get strategy recommendations

### Claude Validation Queue (4 endpoints)
- `POST /api/claude/enqueue` - Add validation request
- `GET /api/claude/queue/status` - Get queue status & metrics
- `GET /api/claude/performance` - Get performance stats
- `GET/POST /api/claude/settings` - Get/update settings

### Signal Scanning (1 endpoint)
- `POST /api/scan` - Run market scan (enhanced with queue)

**Total: 15 new endpoints + 5 legacy = 20 endpoints**

