## ğŸš§ Known Limitations

### Current Constraints
1. **Free Tier Limits:**
   - TwelveData: 800 API calls/day
   - Only 5-minute base data (resampled to other timeframes)
   - 4 symbols tracked (EUR/USD, GBP/USD, XAU/USD, USOIL)

2. **Claude API:**
   - Default quota: 20 validations/day (configurable)
   - 2-5 second validation time per signal
   - Cost per validation (depends on usage plan)

3. **Signal Frequency:**
   - Elliott Wave patterns are rare
   - 1-3 qualified signals per day typical
   - High-score signals (â‰¥150) very rare

